  <div class="tip-overview text-content">
    <h4>Overview</h4>
    <h1 class="summary-rec">Reduce the load times of pages by storing commonly used files from your website
on your visitors browser.</h1>
<ul>
  <li>Reduce page load times for repeat visitors</li>
  <li>Particularly effective on websites where users regularly re-visit the same areas of the website</li>
  <li>Cost-benefit ratio: high</li>
  <li>Access needed</li>
</ul>

  </div>
</div>

